    <!-- LITTLE PUMA -->
    <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
      Little PUMA: Calibration Device
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>
        I joined the team at the start of the development of PUMA’s calibration device, a project
        which I led from initial development through testing.
      </p>

      <p>
        Two grids are mounted inside PUMA’s drift region. Some electrons are stopped by the grid
        mesh; grid transparency is defined as the fraction of electrons that pass through. Accurate
        calibration of this transparency is required for precise PUMA measurements.
      </p>
    </div>

